OL,3,CPolice told to scale back arrests in
OL,4,Cbid to cut prison overcrowding,
OL,5,Creports say
OL,7,Fare reportedly being advised to arrest
OL,8,Ffewer people in a bid to ease
OL,9,Fovercrowding in prisons.
OL,11,FForce chiefs are being told to
OL,12,Fconsider halting "non-priority
OL,13,Farrests" until there is capacity in
OL,14,FEngland and Wales's jails, The Times
OL,15,Freported.
