OL,3,CPolice told to scale back arrests in
OL,4,Cbid to cut prison overcrowding,
OL,5,Creports say
OL,7,FThe newspaper said it obtained an
OL,8,Finternal document from the National
OL,9,FPolice Chiefs' Council (NPCC) which
OL,10,Falso said "any planned operations
OL,11,Fwhere large numbers of arrests may
OL,12,Ftake place" should potentially be
OL,13,Fpaused to ease pressures in the
OL,14,Fcriminal justice system.
OL,16,FThis is thought to apply to operations
OL,17,Fthat do not have to happen on a
OL,18,Fspecific date and could be arranged
OL,19,Ffor a later time.
