OL,3,CPolice told to scale back arrests in
OL,4,Cbid to cut prison overcrowding,
OL,5,Creports say
OL,7,FThe news is likely to heap pressure on
OL,8,FRishi Sunak's government, which has
OL,9,Frecently come under fire over a policy
OL,10,Fto free criminals from jail early and
OL,11,Fdelays to court cases as part of
OL,12,Fefforts to cut prison overcrowding.
OL,14,FFirst announced last year, the
OL,15,Fgovernment insisted the early release
OL,16,Fscheme would be temporary and would
OL,17,Fonly allow "low-level offenders" out
OL,18,Fof prison up to 18 days early under
OL,19,Fstrict supervision.
