OL,3,CPolice told to scale back arrests in
OL,4,Cbid to cut prison overcrowding,
OL,5,Creports say
OL,7,FBut earlier this month, it emerged
OL,8,Fthat ministers were preparing to
OL,9,Fextend the scheme for a second time so
OL,10,Fsome criminals could be freed from
OL,11,Fjail up to 70 days before their
OL,12,Frelease date. This is expected to take
OL,13,Feffect from Thursday.
OL,15,FLabour said the Tories'
OL,16,F"mismanagement" of the criminal
OL,17,Fjustice system "cannot go on".
