OL,3,CPolice told to scale back arrests in
OL,4,Cbid to cut prison overcrowding,
OL,5,Creports say
OL,7,FA separate, internal letter from the
OL,8,FNPCC to chief constables in England
OL,9,Fand Wales, seen by The Times, warned
OL,10,Fthat the government's contingency
OL,11,Fmeasures are having an "unsustainable
OL,12,Foperational impact on policing", risk
OL,13,Fpublic safety and could limit
OL,14,Fofficers' ability to investigate crime.
OL,16,FThe paper said the memo also warned of
OL,17,Fthe risk of suspects suing police
OL,18,Fforces for unlawful detention due to
OL,19,Fthe knock-on effects of the Ministry
OL,20,Fof Justice's so-called Operation Early
OL,21,FDawn.
